What you need to know:

Liverpool boss Klopp highlighted the large number of penalties given to United since Solskjaer took charge in a rant that following the champions not getting a spot-kick in Monday's defeat at SouthamptonUnited have been awarded six league penalties this season compared to the five won by Klopp's menThey have been given 42 in all competitions since Solskjaer took over in December 2018 compared to Liverpool's 19 in the same period